Web Services are all about providing a web API for your web application, and are typically implemented in either [REST|http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Representational_State_Transfer] or [SOAP|http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SOAP], though there are many others, like [RSS|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/RSS] and [ATOM|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Atom_(standard)].
